Content:
stormasm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5919] updated crate thiserror to version 1.0.31 in four crates
merelymyself 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5916] ensured 
``required``
 positionals don't show up as 
``optional``
 when 
``help``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5890] Better error handling using 
``do``
WindSoilder created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5913] make module imports in scripts used for relative path.
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5886] make path exists work on expanded path
Kangaxx-0 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5911] added all flag to nu-check command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5864] Introduce new command - nu check
Yethal 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5910] slimmed down Dockerfile
CBenoit created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5909] docs: clarify 
``print``
 and 
``echo``
 commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5889] build: update 
``miette``
 dependency
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5885] feat: add 
``--binary(-b)``
 option to 
``hash``
 commands
nibon7 created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5908] Return error when external command core dumped
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5905] fixed bug where 
``thin``
 theme wasn't getting applied correctly
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5901] fix excessive ansi escape sequences
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5881] update encode decode with new signature
elferherrera created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5896] Header filtering out of for loop
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5892] Dataframe with real index
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5891] Remove extra print
rgwood created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/5893] Make sort logic available outside sort-by
